These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, strawberry
House: tower, colonial
2 different games are played: chess, billiard
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, indian
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, grey
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, iris
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, march
1. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the indian is on the left of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Food      | strawberry     | apple |
| House         | colonial  | tower       |
| Game           | billiard   | chess    |
| Nationality   | indian     | australian   |
| Color   | grey      | red     |
| Flower         | iris | daffodil      |
| Birthday     | march       | december           |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different games are played: snooker, backgammon
City: san-francisco, paris
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, climbing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil
House: art-deco, futuristic
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, february
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, d&b
1. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
4. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Game      | backgammon         | snooker       |
| City          | san-francisco        | paris |
| Sport           | climbing | volleyball    |
| Flower   | daffodil        | azalea  |
| House   | futuristic        | art-deco       |
| Birthday           | february            | march        |
| Music-Genre     | d&b            | disco       |

